            If the Government propose a fair system, such as a system of match funding&#x2014;I think the Liberal Democrats would agree with that, and many Conservative Members would go along with it&#x2014;they will find that they have a huge amount of support and win the argument. Already, the pass has been sold on
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_275wh' title='Col. 275WH &mdash; HC Deb 26 June 2002 vol 387 c275WH' name='column_275wh' href='#column_275wh' rel='bookmark'>275WH</a>
